# ─── idastone repo .gitignore ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file protects the idastone repo itself from accidental leakage by
# contributors. For the file that gets merged into a USER's project on
# install, see install-assets/gitignore.idastone.

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/

# Node
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.claude/settings.local.json
.cursor/
.continue/
.aider*

# ─── Secrets — never commit any of these, ever ────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
id_rsa
id_rsa.*
id_ed25519
id_ed25519.*
id_ecdsa
id_ecdsa.*
.netrc
.ssh/
credentials.json
credentials.yaml
secrets/
*.secret
*.secrets
service-account*.json
gcp-*.json
aws-credentials*
known_hosts

# ─── ML / research artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never commit checkpoints, trained weights, or large data.
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.safetensors
*.onnx
*.bin
*.npz
*.npy
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.arrow
*.parquet
checkpoints/
data/
datasets/
wandb/
mlruns/
outputs/
lightning_logs/

# ─── Harness runtime — never commit (per-project state) ──────────────────
**/.claude/memory/workflow.db
**/.claude/memory/workflow.db-*
**/.claude/memory/hook.log*
**/.claude/memory/ntfy_last_seen
**/.claude/.state/clean-ok-*
.team-runs/

# Per-project autopilot config is shell-sourced → never commit
**/.claude/autopilot.conf
**/.claude/budget.toml
**/.claude/project_id

# User-global Claude Code cache dirs — belt-and-suspenders, should never
# appear in a project repo anyway
.claude/file-history/
.claude/session-env/
.claude/history.jsonl

# ─── Agent scratch — anything the agent needs but shouldn't share ────────
# The canonical location for per-project agent state that is NOT part of
# the harness (e.g. temp plots, draft findings, in-progress research notes).
.claude/_local/

# ─── User-confidential — stays on your box ───────────────────────────────
# Convention: any dir or file named _private or _internal at any depth
# is treated as "not for sharing." Drop your lab's NDA notes, unreleased
# results, or competitive positioning here.
_private/
**/_private/
docs/_internal/
**/*.private.md
NOTES_PRIVATE*

# Logs
*.log
logs/
